11:00.325 --> 11:02.660
Um, sorry, Ms. Akino, just Preston.

11:02.728 --> 11:04.729
"Preston," huh?

11:04.796 --> 11:06.397
Not "Mr. Terry"?

11:10.068 --> 11:11.502
I've received hundreds of calls

11:11.570 --> 11:14.435
asking why Beck hasn't been arrested.
How would you answer?

11:14.497 --> 11:17.541
Well, we're still in the early stages
of the investigation.

11:17.609 --> 11:19.343
He's on video saying he has

11:19.411 --> 11:20.978
a license to kill white people.

11:21.046 --> 11:22.813
The video may speak to motive, ma'am,

11:22.881 --> 11:24.381
but it's not grounds for an arrest.

11:24.449 --> 11:25.883
I need to prove he acted willfully

11:25.951 --> 11:27.051
beyond a reasonable doubt.

11:27.119 --> 11:28.853
And how long will that take?

11:28.920 --> 11:31.675
Ma'am, do you want this done right
or do you want this done quickly?

11:31.723 --> 11:34.625
I'm expecting you to do both.

11:34.693 --> 11:36.894
If Deputy Beck intentionally
victimized Jesse

11:36.962 --> 11:38.452
because of bias, he will be indicted.

11:38.547 --> 11:41.315
And if he acted in self-defense,
then he'll be cleared.

11:41.383 --> 11:43.050
The truth is my only compass.

11:43.118 --> 11:45.152
That's a nice compass to have.

11:45.220 --> 11:47.254
I don't have the luxury of getting lost.

11:47.322 --> 11:49.090
