of this state.

11:49.157 --> 11:50.257
Neither do I.

11:50.325 --> 11:52.326
I'd like to invite you

11:52.394 --> 11:54.261
to an event tomorrow night as my guest.

11:54.329 --> 11:56.420
I'd be honored, Governor, but my father,

11:56.498 --> 11:59.256
- he's, he's in from out of town...
- The invitation extends to him as well.

12:00.769 --> 12:02.536
Thank you, ma'am.

12:02.604 --> 12:04.338
Well, I'm pleased that the governor came

12:04.406 --> 12:05.806
to show her support

12:05.874 --> 12:07.842
for Alicia Carr and her son Jesse.

12:07.909 --> 12:10.211
No mother should have to bury a child.

12:10.278 --> 12:13.681
