14:07.095 --> 14:08.662
42, get over here!

14:10.565 --> 14:13.539
This is a 25-yarder.
You can do this in your sleep.

14:13.640 --> 14:15.603
- Yes, Coach.
- Go.

14:15.670 --> 14:16.837
Tommy!

14:18.106 --> 14:19.707
Your black ass better block her

14:19.775 --> 14:22.176
