14:23.345 --> 14:24.545
- Yes, Coach!
- Go!

14:26.548 --> 14:28.115
(cheering)

14:30.685 --> 14:32.019
Hut!

14:35.924 --> 14:38.359
(cheering)

14:45.467 --> 14:46.500
AKINO: Volunteer coach.

14:46.568 --> 14:48.202
