15:02.517 --> 15:03.450
Any ideas?

15:03.518 --> 15:04.819
No.

15:04.886 --> 15:07.755
Like you said, y'all are family.

15:07.823 --> 15:10.024
And nobody hurts you like your own.

15:10.091 --> 15:12.593
I'm gonna go celebrate with my team now.

15:14.930 --> 15:17.170
Why did you threaten Shameeka
after her son was murdered?

15:17.232 --> 15:18.432
Excuse me?

15:18.500 --> 15:19.667
Joey Campbell's mother.

15:19.734 --> 15:21.602
- You got some balls on you.
- Thank you.

15:21.670 --> 15:22.870
You got an answer?

15:24.439 --> 15:26.340
Joey was a drug dealer and she knew it

15:26.408 --> 15:28.309
and she did nothing, and now he is dead.

15:28.376 --> 15:32.446
I don't want to see her other son
end up the same way.

15:32.514 --> 15:34.281
I was trying to scare her straight.

15:49.710 --> 15:51.131
Hey.

15:51.199 --> 15:52.466
How you doing?

15:52.534 --> 15:54.561
I'm all right.

15:55.604 --> 15:57.238
It's tough, though, man.

15:57.305 --> 16:02.977
