to our families, no matter what.

16:03.044 --> 16:04.311
Yeah.

16:05.680 --> 16:09.183
- So you want to kill crackers, huh?
- The video was a joke.

16:09.251 --> 16:11.185
I ain't laughing.

16:11.253 --> 16:12.753
Mind getting the hell out of my way?

16:12.821 --> 16:13.821
No, Beck.

16:13.855 --> 16:14.855
